    passage: "An airline introduced a policy allowing passengers to board in the order they arrive at the gate, rather than by assigned zones. After the change, the average time to board a full flight decreased by four minutes. An analyst wants to determine whether the new boarding policy, rather than some other factor, was responsible for the improvement.",
